<a name="faq"></a>
<h2>FAQs</h2>
<ul>
  <li>What license?
  <p>The <a href="http://www.opensource.org/licenses/gpl-license.php">GPL</a>.
  <li>What platforms does it work on?
  <p>It should work on any platform where spidermonkey runs.  I've only tested
     on Linux, though.
  <li>Why?
  <p>I wanted a way to interpret JavaScript with minimal dependencies, and to
     easily expose a Python DOM to JavaScript.  This is used by
     <a href="../DOMForm/">DOMForm</a>.
</ul>

